---
title: Korean Beef Bibimbap With Zucchini, Mushrooms, Carrots
description: This dish takes its name from the Korean word for mixing rice. When you're ready to eat, put your rice in a bowl, add the toppings, and mix them together so that the flavours and textures combine in a glorious mishmash!
